Package: citapir
Type: Package
Title: Synchronized Online Bibliography in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Patrice Godard
Maintainer: Patrice Godard <patrice.godard@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides a way to maintain a synchronized version
   of Zotero (http://zotero.org)
   and Mendeley (https://www.mendeley.com) bibliography.
Depends:
   R (>= 3.6),
   httr,
   tibble,
   dplyr,
   magrittr,
Imports:
   glue
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
